    h2.f2.tc With Our Powers Combined...
    p.f3 Like anything, Coalescence is what you make it. We ask that every Coalescee contribute somewhow--whether its leading an activity, picking up trash, helping coordinate a meal, organizing a gear exchange or throwing a camp party!
